Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:59.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx130\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,170.389)}Gel Shocker's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,710.389)}Deliveryman of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hosoya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When did it get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:39.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We of Gel Shocker mourn the\Ndeath of Hosoya Tsutomu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,head of the Japanese Industrial Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,November 25th at midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The 25th is tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would play such a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die... that is why I am here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosoya Tsutomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Death itself is here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're on Gel Shocker's\Ndeath list, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, Spiderlion, am your executioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster... it's trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker always gets what it wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The first page of the\Nassassination list is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Operation: T3...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, your plan to assassinate\Nthe leaders in various fields across Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,has been analyzed\Ncarefully by our computers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The tests have already been run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that my plan is approved,\NI'll move it into action in force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See that it is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And deploy Gel Shocker's robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Page two of the assassination list
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,begins with the chair of the Japanese\NScience Academy Cooperative,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Aono Kiyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, all right.\N- Your car is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Has someone passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's just playing a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It says I'm going to die in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Modern science isn't advanced enough to\Npredict the hour of a person's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Gel Shocker...\Nnow they're after Doctor Aono?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered that my little brother was\Na member of the Kamen Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. \NSo, where's Doctor Aono now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The academy meeting\Nshould be over now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be heading home around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty minutes until his predicted death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's Gel Shocker we're dealing with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to assume they'll\Ngo through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, we should contact Captain\NTaki and Mr. Hongo at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. This isn't the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the right way, Doctor Aono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of your death\Nis five minutes from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You... are you planning to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stop talking now, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leading him to the designated location for\Nthe second entry on the assassination list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Everything is in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,General, someone's tailing the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the combatants in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two blips will be Taki and Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one minute to the time\NGel Shocker predicted for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Hey, it's turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Aono, we're here to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to safety, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Aono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Aono,\Nyour death will come right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Aono!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gel Shocker cyborg, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Combining the physical strength of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a lion and the abilities\Nof a spider... Spiderlion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not on the assassination list,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will deal with you, regardless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one behind the\Npredicted assassinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing Gel Shocker cannot do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:24.55,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try to interfere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but our assassinations\Nwill continue unabated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, where's Doctor Aono?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll stop their next\Npredicted assassination!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I dozed off there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The third person on Gel Shocker's\Nassassination list is Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight at midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I make reservations\Nat the temple, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, this is no time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't sound so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't underestimate that Spiderlion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiderlion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our best chance to take\Nout Spiderlion once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We should move Pops to a safe place first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's going to play out the\Nsame no matter where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be that easy to fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if we stay here and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust my life to your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. I'm going to check\Non things out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Nobody came at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They got us all riled up for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But Gel Shocker wouldn't make\Nthat prediction for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That message was about tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a cruel prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:17.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnOne Stroke Script LET\fad(1700,0)\fs80\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hongo Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hongo Takeshi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's real target is Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Spiderlion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... he's here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take me to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiderlion... show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.92,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:22.77,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The third entry on the assassination\Nlist is not Tachibana Tobei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:31.36,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The name on the third page,\NKamen Rider... is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you lured me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now take you to Gel Shocker's\N13th execution cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your death will come\Nat 6:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice rest with that\Nsleeping gas in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Damn.\N- Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! You can't mean to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we'd hesitate to kill you\Nif it meant killing the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy a nice, leisurely death, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the ceiling and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the Kamen Rider could escape\NGel Shocker's predicted assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your predicted assassination\Nhas failed, Spiderlion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you survive being\Nskewered by the spikes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can easily break spikes\Nas brittle as these!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:07.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:14.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:18.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:22.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:56.10,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:22:03.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:07.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:15.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:41.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Swimming through the\Noceans with a Rider Swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:49.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great dive flitting\Nthrough the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:52.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up whirlpools\Nwith a Rider Screw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:56.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Dragging enemies down\Nwith a Rider Lung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:00.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:04.80,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That trick won't work a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... this time, I will end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Flying Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.32,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider could not afford to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.63,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,He foiled Gel Shocker's assassination plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:03.12,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,and kept his promise to keep us safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:04.22,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Ride on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:07.74,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Maintain your forward momentum\Nto protect justice and peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,80,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone. Hongo Takeshi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:17.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's hear about next week's\Nstory from Director Tsukada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:21.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week's story is about Catgecko, a\Nmonster that can jump out of paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:23.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do any of you have paintings\Nof cats in your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:31.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monstrous Catgecko might\Njust jump out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:31.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(667.167,350.389)}Eerie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:31.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs115\bord0.8\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}The Bloodthirsty Black Cat Paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:50.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:01.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:05.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:09.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:13.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's Deliveryman of Death!
Comment: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eerie - The Bloodthirsty Black Cat Paintings!\NThe story of the monster Catgecko who\Njumps out of paintings will be scary.